Maintainer: Rory Nolan <rorynoolan@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/rorynolan/filesstrings
BugReports: https://github.com/rorynolan/filesstrings/issues
Description: This package is gives functions for calculation of molecular 
    number and brightness from images, as detailed in Digman et al. 2008. This
    is the first free, open-source software available for this purpose and comes
    with an implementation of the novel "automatic detrending" technique.
